rdan-belfort-downplays-trump-tariff-concerns-calls-democratic-criticism-complete-utter-nonsense%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox%20%26amp%3B%20Friends%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20come%20as%20the%20stock%20market%20reels%20from%20concerns%20over%20a%20trade%20war.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20closed%20in%20correction%20territory%2C%20reflecting%20investor%20anxiety%20over%20Trump's%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20steel%20and%20aluminium%20imports%20and%20a%20proposed%20200%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20European%20champagne%20and%20alcohol%20products.%20Canada%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20have%20already%20vowed%20retaliatory%20tariffs%2C%20deepening%20fears%20of%20an%20economic%20standoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20market%20reaction%2C%20Trump%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20bend%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%20Defending%20the%20policy%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fstory%2Finternational%2Ftrump-vows-to-take-back-stolen-wealth-as-tariffs-on-steel-and-aluminum-imports-go-into-effect%2F2370567%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20take%20back%20our%20wealth%2C%20and%20we're%20going%20to%20take%20back%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20companies%20that%20left.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelfort%20echoed%20this%2C%20saying%20that%20restoring%20domestic%20production%20was%20essential%20for%20the%20US%20economy.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20be%20a%20consumer%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20being%20on%20a%20sugar%20high%20for%2050%20years.%20At%20some%20point%2C%20you're%20bleeding%20the%20wealth%20out%20of%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomists%20have%20warned%20that%20tariffs%20could%20raise%20costs%20for%20consumers%20and%20strain%20global%20trade%20relations%2C%20to%20which%20Belfort%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20only%20people%20who%20are%20panicking%20are%20probably%2C%20you%20know%2C%20on%20CNBC%20trying%20to%20make%20everyone%20panic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20suggested%20that%20opponents%20of%20Trump's%20policies%20would%20criticise%20him%20no%20matter%20what.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20he%20does%2C%20they're%20gonna%20say%20they%20hate%20it%2C%20'it's%20the%20worst%20thing%20in%20the%20world.'%20...%20You%20start%20to%20just%20ignore%20it.%20It's%20complete%20and%20utter%20nonsense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20didn't%20have%20tariffs%2C%20they%20would%20be%20saying%2C%20'How%20could%20he%20not%20be%20addressing%20tariffs%3F!%20He%20has%20to%20put%20tariffs%20on%20things.%20Everyone%20is%20taking%20advantage%20of%20us!'%26quot%3B%20he%20went%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20same%20Fox%20%26amp%3B%20Friends%20appearance%2C%20Belfort%20also%20heaped%20praise%20on%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bhero%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20promising%20to%20purchase%20a%20Tesla%20that%20very%20day.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20gonna%20buy%20a%20Tesla%20today%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared%2C%20earning%20a%20nod%20from%20co-host%20Brian%20Kilmeade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Tesla%20sales%20declining%20globally%20amid%20Elon%20Musk's%20controversial%20political%20shift%20and%20worker%20protests%20at%20US%20dealerships%2C%20Trump%20recently%20promoted%20the%20automaker%20at%20the%20White%20House.%20Turning%20the%20South%20Lawn%20into%20a%20Tesla%20showroom%2C%20Trump%20called%20Musk%20his%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20buddy%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-buys-tesla-elon-musk-helps-him-pick-get-in-patriots-7904284%5C%22%3Ebought%20a%20Tesla%20himself%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20warned%20that%20anyone%20caught%20vandalising%20the%20cars%20could%20be%20labelled%20a%20%26quot%3Bdomestic%20terrorist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJordan%20Belfort%20was%20convicted%20of%20securities%20fraud