t%20has%20not%20posed%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20Pakistan.%20The%20movement%20has%20maintained%20unity%20and%20focus%2C%20with%20various%20factions%20operating%20without%20internal%20divisions.%20Alongside%20militant%20insurgents%2C%20rights%20groups%20have%20also%20been%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20Activists%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20Karima%20Baloch%2C%20former%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Baloch%20Students%20Organization-Azad%20(BSO-Azad)%2C%20advocated%20for%20Baloch%20rights%20and%20independence%20despite%20living%20in%20exile%20in%20Canada%20due%20to%20threats%20and%20state%20persecution.%20Even%20from%20abroad%2C%20she%20remained%20a%20powerful%20international%20voice%20for%20the%20Baloch%20cause.%20Her%20mysterious%20death%20in%20Toronto%20in%20December%202020%E2%80%94widely%20suspected%20by%20Baloch%20activists%20to%20be%20an%20assassination%20orchestrated%20by%20Pakistani%20intelligence%20agencies%E2%80%94became%20a%20rallying%20point%20for%20the%20Baloch%20diaspora%2C%20bringing%20global%20attention%20to%20their%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20prominent%20activist%20is%20Mahrang%20Baloch%2C%20a%20young%20doctor%20and%20human%20rights%20advocate%20who%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20leading%20figure%20in%20the%20current%20Baloch%20rights%20movement.%20Known%20for%20her%20protests%20against%20enforced%20disappearances%E2%80%94particularly%20after%20her%20father%20was%20abducted%20and%20killed%20by%20security%20forces%E2%80%94she%20and%20many%20others%20call%20for%20provincial%20autonomy%2C%20devolution%20of%20education%20and%20social%20justice%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20peaceful%20resolution%20to%20Balochistan's%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Baloch%20Movement%20Really%20Is%20About%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20highlight%20these%20figures%20because%2C%20amid%20the%20recent%20train%20hijacking%20and%20the%20alleged%20killing%20of%20several%20Pakistani%20servicemen%2C%20many%20may%20have%20overlooked%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Baloch%20independence%20movement%20is%20not%20solely%20about%20violent%20separatism.%20A%20non-militant%20front%20has%20long%20been%20active%2C%20though%20the%20Pakistani%20establishment%20and%20deep%20state%20have%20largely%20ignored%20it.%20It%20often%20takes%20a%20high-profile%20act%20of%20violence%E2%80%94such%20as%209%2F11%2C%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20or%20the%20December%2016%2C%202014%2C%20Peshawar%20Army%20School%20attack%E2%80%94to%20jolt%20a%20state%20into%20acknowledging%20an%20emerging%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BLA's%20hijacking%20of%20the%20Jaffar%20Express%20on%20March%2013%20and%20the%20alleged%20killing%20of%20numerous%20Pakistani%20security%20personnel%20after%20the%20release%20of%20innocent%20passengers%20have%20given%20the%20militant%20separatist%20movement%20in%20Balochistan%20unprecedented%20momentum.%20This%20event%20was%20designed%20for%20mass%20impact%2C%20much%20like%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack%20in%C2%A0%202023%20at%20the%20Gaza-Israel%20border%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%201%2C200%20deaths%20and%20nearly%20250%20hostages%20being%20taken.%20Just%20as%20Hamas%20sought%20to%20revive%20the%20Palestinian%20issue%20amid%20concerns%20that%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%20would%20sideline%20it%2C%20the%20BLA%20aimed%20to%20reinvigorate%20the%20Baloch%20separatist%20movement%20and%20prevent%20it%20from%20losing%20steam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAggression%20Can't%20Be%20Default%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20Baloch%20may%20have%20perceived%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20terrorist%20attacks%20by%20the%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%20as%20a%20competing%20force%20dominating%20Pakistan's%20security%20landscape.%20With%20the%20world%20at%20a%20crossroads%20in%20an%20unpredictable%20new%20order%2C%20the%20BLA's%20actions%20were%20intended%20to%20attract%20global%20attention%20and%20sympathy.%20However%2C%20such%20a%20bold%20move%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20provoke%20a%20severe%20and%20prolonged%20response%20from%20Pakistan's%20political%20and%20security%20establishment%E2%80%94an%20approach%20that%20has%20historically%20been%20its%20default%20response%2C%20rather%20than%20seeking%20dialogue%20or%20negotiation.%20This%20very%20mindset%20led%20to%20the%20separation%20of%20Bangladesh%20in%201971%2C%20as%20Pakistan%20failed%20to%20recognise%20the%20power%20of%20the%20people%20or%20its%20own%20shortcomings%20in%20crisis%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20violence%20or%20to%20the%20aggressive%20responses%20it%20has%20traditionally%20favoured.%20However%2C%20Balochistan's%20terrain%20does%20not%20lend%20itself%20to%20an%20easy%20counterinsurgency%20fight%E2%80%94any%20military%20engagement%20risks%20entangling%20Pakistan%20in%20an%20extended%2C%20unwinnable%20conflict.%20Deploying%20additional%20troops%2C%20helicopters%2C%20and%20other%20force%20multipliers%20creates%20vulnerable%20assets%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20given%20that%20Balochistan%20makes%20up%20over%2040%25%20of%20Pakistan's%20territory%2C%20the%20state%20cannot%20effectively%20control%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%20Lessons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20experience%20dealing%20with%20separatist%20militancy%20and%20terrorism%2C%20but%20it%20has%20never%20succeeded%20in%20completely%20neutralising%20such%20movements.%20The%20most%20glaring%20example%20is%20East%20Pakistan%E2%80%94now%20Bangladesh%E2%80%94where%20Yahya%20Khan's%20heavy-handed%20approach%20led%20to%20the%20region's%20eventual%20secession.%20The%20Pakistan%20Army's%20leadership%20has%20long%20been%20steeped%20in%20a%20culture%20of%20machismo%2C%20believing%20that%20applying%20greater%20force%20than%20the%20adversary%20will%20resolve%20all%20problems.%20This%20approach%20offers%20temporary%20reprieve%20at%20best%E2%80%94never%20a%20permanent%20solution.%20Yahya%20Khan%20followed%20it%20in%201971%2C%20with%20disastrous%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20dynamic%20unfolded%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20(KP)%2C%20where%20the%20military%20deployed%20helicopter%20gunships%2C%20tanks%2C%20and%20artillery%2C%20razing%20entire%20villages%20to%20deny%20the%20TTP%20its%20support%20base.%20Operation%20Zarb-e-Azb%20(2014%E2%80%932018)%20brought%20temporary%20peace%2C%20but%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20mistakenly%20believed%20it%20had%20achieved%20lasting%20success.%20The%20flaw%20in%20Pakistan's%20counterinsurgency%20doctrine%20is%20its%20failure%20to%20grasp%20the%20nuances%20of%20conflict%20resolution%20and%20termination.%20This%20is%20evident%20not%20only%20in%20asymmetric%20warfare%20but%20also%20in%20conventional%20military%20strategy%E2%80%94seen%20most%20notably%20in%20the%20Kargil%20conflict%2C%20where%20General%20Pervez%20Musharraf%20miscalculated%20that%20surprise%20and%20deception%20would%20secure%20Pakistan%20a%20victory.%20He%20failed%20to%20anticipate%20India's%20professional%20and%20determined%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20now%20faces%20a%20similarly%20grave%20miscalculation%20in%20Balochistan.%20Whether%20it%20acknowledges%20it%20or%20not%2C%20the%20situation%20demands%20more%20than%20just%20brute%20force%E2%80%94it%20requires%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20in%20strategy%2C%20one%20that%20prioritises%20political%20engagement%20over%20military%20suppression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20TTP%20Experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20temporary%20lull%20in%20the%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan's%20(TTP)%20operations%20led%20to%20the%20flawed%20assumption%20that%20it%20had%20been%20defeated.%20In%20reality%2C%20the%20TTP's%20core%20sustenance%20and%20support%20came%20from%20across%20the%20border%20in%20Afghanistan.%20It%20was%20revived%20the%20moment%20the%20Taliban%20began%20pursuing%20broader%20ambitions%20of%20establishing%20their%20version%20of%20Islamic%20dominance%20in%20the%20region.%20Now%2C%20the%20TTP%20is%20back%20in%20full%20force%2C%20adding%20to%20Pakistan's%20woes.%20A%20similar%20resurgence%20could%20occur%20if%20Pakistan's%20only%20response%20to%20the%20Baloch%20Liberation%20Army's%20(BLA)%20actions%20is%20military%20and%20kinetic%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20meaningful%20outreach%20to%20the%20local%20population%20and%20concrete%20efforts%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20Balochistan%20receives%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20national%20resources%2C%20the%20separatist%20movement%20is%20unlikely%20to%20weaken.%20Similar%20grievances%20exist%20in%20Sindh%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%20and%20Gilgit-Baltistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Balochistan%2C%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20(KP)%20does%20not%20have%20an%20active%2C%20organised%20separatist%20movement.%20The%20Pashtun%20Tahafuz%20Movement%20(PTM)%20is%20not%20separatist%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20is%20a%20civil%20rights%20movement%20that%20emerged%20in%20KP%20and%20the%20former%20Federally%20Administered%20Tribal%20Areas%20(FATA)%2C%20advocating%20for%20Pashtun%20rights%2C%20accountability%20for%20military%20operations%2C%20and%20an%20end%20to%20enforced%20disappearances.%20Although%20the%20state%20frequently%20accuses%20PTM%20of%20separatist%20tendencies%2C%20the%20movement%20itself%20denies%20any%20such%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThings%20Can%20Spiral%20Out%20Of%20Control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20TTP's%20primary%20objective%20is%20to%20establish%20Sharia%20law%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20replacing%20the%20country's%20democratic%20system%20with%20a%20Taliban-style%20Islamic%20Emirate%20governed%20by%20their%20interpretation%20of%20Sharia.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20Baloch%20separatism%20gaining%20momentum%2C%20a%20knee-jerk%20military%20response%E2%80%94Pakistan's%20default%20approach%E2%80%94is%20likely%20to%20trigger%20a%20spiral%20of%20violence%20that%20will%20be%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20control.%20Coupled%20with%20the%20persistent%20threat%20of%20TTP%20attacks%20and%20ongoing%20military%20operations%20along%20the%20Durand%20Line%20to%20maintain%20border%20sanctity%2C%20Pakistan's%20security%20forces%20are%20preparing%20for%20a%20prolonged%20period%20of%20active%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20escalation%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20economic%20indicators%20suggest%20Pakistan%20is%20beginning%20to%20stabilise%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%203%25%20GDP%20growth%20rate%20this%20year.%20However%2C%20prolonged%20military%20commitments%20could%20significantly%20undermine%20these%20gains.%20During%20Operation%20Zarb-e-Azb%2C%20nearly%20one-third%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Army's%20active%20infantry%20formations%20were%20engaged%20in%20counterterrorism%20operations.%20Given%20its%20current%20360-degree%20security%20threats%2C%20Pakistan's%20deep%20state%20may%20seek%20alternative%20strategies%2C%20including%20diversions%20it%20believes%20are%20manageable%20and%20within%20India's%20threshold%20of%20tolerance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20today's%20evolving%20geopolitical%20landscape%2C%20banking%20on%20such%20a%20strategy%20without%20accurately%20assessing%20India's%20potential%20response%20would%20be%20a%20risky%20gamble.%20India%20must%20remain%20vigilant%20against%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccopycat%E2%80%9D%20deniable%20act%20of%20terror%E2%80%94one%20that%20could%20blend%20elements%20of%20recent%20trends%20in%20transnational%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20writer%20is%20a%20Member%20of%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%2C%20Chancellor%20of%20the%20Central%20University%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Former%20GOC%20of%20the%20Srinagar-based%2015%20Corps.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742197020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.gadgets360cdn.com%2Flarge%2Fpakistan_the_artist_studio_unspl