0the%20%26quot%3Bright%20to%20development%20claims%20equal%20priority%20(to%20the%20right%20to%20a%20clean%20environment)%20under%20the%20fundamental%20rights%26quot%3B%20and%20overturned%20the%20April%202022%20order%20by%20the%20NGT's%20Southern%20Zone%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20struck%20down%20that%20order%2C%20saying%20it%20had%20been%20passed%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20jurisdiction%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Blegally%20untenable%26quot%3B.%20The%20court%20said%20no%20case%20for%20violation%20of%20any%20law%20had%20been%20made%20out%20with%20respect%20to%20required%20environmental%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Justice%20Trivedi%20also%20underlined%20the%20%26quot%3Bneed%20for%20sustainable%20development%20(that)%20strikes%20a%20golden%20balance%20between%20the%20right%20to%20development%20and%20the%20right%20to%20a%20clean%20environment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGT%20order%20had%20been%20passed%20after%20an%20appeal%20by%20Navroz%20Kerasp%20Mody%20that%20challenged%20the%20cutting%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20trees%20by%20the%20Auroville%20Foundation.%20The%20argument%20was%20that%20the%20area%20constituted%20a%20'forest'%20and%20the%20township's%20'development'%20plans%20would%20destroy%20the%20green%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuroville%2C%20though%2C%20had%20argued%20it%20had%20been%20developed%20as%20an%20'international%20cultural%20township'%20and%20could%20not%2C%20therefore%2C%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20forest%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGT%20then%20directed%20the%20Foundation%20to%20file%20a%20plan%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20proposed%20construction%20work%2C%20which%20included%20ring%20roads%20and%20industrial%20areas.%20The%20Foundation%20was%20also%20told%20to%20get%20environmental%20clearances.%20All%20work%20had%20been%20halted%20till%20these%20requirements%20were%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuroville%20claims%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Buniversal%20town%20where%20men%20and%20women%20of%20all%20countries%20are%20able%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20and%20progressive%20harmony%20above%20all%20creeds%2C%20all%20politics%20and%20all%20nationalities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20website%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20Auroville%20is%20%26quot%3Bto%20realise%20human%20unity%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20around%2050%2C000%20people%20from%20around%20the%20world%20who%20live%20in%20Auroville.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20township%20is%C2%A0the%20Matrimandir%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20'the%20soul%20of%20the%20city'%20that%20functions%20as%20a%20place%20for%20meditation%2C%20self-reflection%2C%20and%20prayer.%20Radiating%20out%20beyond%20are%20four%20zones%20-%20Industrial%20(in%20the%20north)%2C%20cultural%20(northeast)%2C%20residential%20(south%2Fsouth%20west)%20and%20international%20(west).%20And%20surrounding%20the%20township%20is%20a%20green%20space%20that%20consists%20of%20forested%20areas%2C%20farms%2C%20and%20sanctuaries.%C2%A0.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742196060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F2j1ianlo_auroville-_650x400_17_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fright-to-development-equally-important-supreme-court-order-on-auroville-7941260%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20set%20aside%20a%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20order%20that%20had%20banned%20the%20Auroville%20Foundation%20from%20undertaking%20'development'%20activities%20within%20its%20township%20in%20Puducherry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fright-to-development-equally-important-supreme-court-order-on-auroville-7941260%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Imran's%20relationship%20with%20Lekha%20sparks%20controversy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742195995000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F