0state%20of%20cricketing%20affairs%20in%20Pakistan%20was%20already%20in%20disarray%2C%20with%20the%20men's%20national%20team%20struggling%20to%20secure%20positive%20results%20on%20international%20cricket.%20And%20now%2C%20the%20losses%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20incurred%20by%20hosting%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20have%20reportedly%20burnt%20a%20big%20hole%20in%20the%20board's%20pocket.%20The%20PCB%20is%20said%20to%20have%20incurred%20a%20mind-boggling%20loss%20of%20USD%2085%20million%20(INR%20869%20crore)%20by%20hosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20a%20tournament%20in%20which%20they%20played%20just%20one%20game%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20suffered%20a%20defeat%20in%20their%20opening%20Group%20A%20match%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Lahore%20before%20travelling%20to%20Dubai%20where%20they%20faced%20India.%20Their%20third%20and%20final%20group%20match%20against%20Bangladesh%20was%20washed%20out%20without%20a%20ball%20being%20bowled.%20Due%20to%20the%20defeats%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20India%2C%20Pakistan%20were%20knocked%20out%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20hence%20ending%20the%20campaign%20with%20just%20one%20home%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fcostliest-home-game-ever-pakistan-spent-inr-869-crore-for-match-against-new-zealand-in-champions-trophy%2Fcid%2F2089025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelegraph%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pakistan%20had%20spent%20about%20PKR%2018%20billion%20(about%20%2458%20million)%20to%20upgrade%20their%20three%20Champions%20Trophy%20venues%20-Rawalpindi%2C%20Lahore%2C%20and%20Karachi.%20The%20cost%20of%20upgradation%20turned%20out%20to%20be%2050%20percent%20more%20than%20the%20anticipated%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20also%20reportedly%20spent%20USD%2040%20million%20on%20event%20preparations.%20In%20return%2C%20however%2C%20their%20earnings%20were%20literally%20in%20pennies.%20PCB%20is%20said%20to%20have%20only%20received%20USD%206%20million%20in%20return%20as%20part%20of%20the%20hosting%20fee.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20ticket%20sales%20and%20sponsorships%2C%20the%20earnings%20were%20negligible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20hence%20concluded%20that%20the%20PCB%20suffered%20a%20loss%20of%20about%20USD%2085%20million%20by%20hosting%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy.%20The%20aftereffects%20of%20such%20a%20loss%20were%20seen%20some%20of%20the%20board's%20subsequent%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20management%20decided%20to%20reduce%20the%20match%20fees%20for%20the%20national%20T20%20championship%20by%2090%20per%20cent%20while%20reducing%20the%20reserve%20player%20payments%20by%2087.5%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Pakistan's%20Dawn%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20PCB%20had%20recently%20reduced%20match%20fees%20from%20Rs%2040%2C000%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20without%20any%20official%20announcement...however%20PCB%20chairman%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20intervened%2C%20rejecting%20the%20decision%20and%20directing%20the%20board's%20domestic%20cricket%20department%20to%20reassess%20the%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%205-star%20accommodations%20for%20players%20were%20swapped%20with%20economy%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742190600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fk20cb41_babar-azam-afp_625x300_23_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fno-more-5-star-hotels-match-fee-cut-as-pcb-suffers-rs-869-crore-loss-in-champions-trophy-report-7940927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20PCB%20has%20reportedly%20suffered%20an%2085%20percent%20loss%20on%20their%20investment%20in%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-c