d%20to%20go%20%E2%80%94%20often%20inspired%20by%20books%20they%20read%20or%20movies%20they%20watched.%20We%20introduced%20a%20fun%20tradition%20to%20let%20them%20have%20a%20say%3A%20writing%20down%20destinations%20on%20chits%20and%20drawing%20a%20winner%20from%20a%20fishbowl.%20Each%20child%20submits%20four%20options%20they%20want%20to%20explore%2C%20and%20we%20draw%20two%20contenders%2C%20assess%20them%20for%20feasibility%20and%20cost%2C%20and%20then%20narrow%20them%20down%20to%20one.%20If%20one%20child's%20pick%20is%20chosen%2C%20the%20other%20takes%20the%20lead%20in%20planning%20the%20itinerary.%20If%20neither%20option%20works%2C%20we%20redraw%20until%20we%20find%20the%20perfect%20fit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20process%20has%20led%20to%20some%20incredible%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sometimes%20unexpected%20%E2%80%94%20escapades%20for%20us.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20ones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8dd5166-035d-49eb-9da4-502f9df50e77%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EFree%20diving%20in%20the%20Great%20Barrier%20Reef%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20of%20my%20kids%20are%20strong%20swimmers%20and%20have%20always%20loved%20the%20ocean.%20Before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20spend%20a%20summer%20exploring%20a%20new%20country%20while%20learning%20to%20surf%2C%20so%20they%20chose%20Australia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20we%20traveled%20to%20cities%20like%20Sydney%20and%20Melbourne%2C%20the%20most%20unforgettable%20experience%20was%20our%20trip%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-barrier-reef-could-disappear-by-2050-why-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Great%20Barrier%20Reef%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Snorkeling%20through%20the%20vibrant%20underwater%20world%2C%20we%20spotted%20reef%20sharks%2C%20clownfish%2C%20and%20groupers.%20The%20true%20highlight%2C%20though%