ker%20sculpture%20in%20all%20three%20parks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20parks%20also%20offer%20seasonal%20events.%20We%20visited%20Legoland%20New%20York%20during%20its%20Brick%20or%20Treat%20Halloween%20special.%20The%20park%20was%20full%20of%20skeletons%20and%20pumpkin%20decorations%20the%20kids%20could%20pose%20with%20and%20play%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20each%20has%20building%20stations%20throughout%20the%20property%20where%20kids%20can%20build%20with%20Lego%20blocks%20and%20earn%20badges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20worth%20staying%20at%20the%20hotel%20no%20matter%20which%20location%20you%20choose.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20Legoland%20hotel%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d3324569253ccddf9932dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20rooms%20at%20Legoland%20hotels%20are%20absolutely%20kid-friendly.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20won't%20lie%2C%20I'm%20a%20sucker%20for%20a%20themed%20anything%2C%20so%20when%20we%20first%20walked%20into%20the%20hotel%20adjacent%20to%20Legoland%20Florida%2C%20I%20was%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel%20is%20decorated%20with%20Lego%20blocks%20and%20even%20has%20pools%20of%20blocks%20kids%20can%20get%20into%20and%20play%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20stay%2C%20we%20stayed%20in%20the%20Legoland%20hotels%20in%20New%20York%20and%20Orlando%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20clear%20that%20the%20rooms%20in%20all%20three%20were%20designed%20with%20family%20in%20mind.%20This%20was%20especially%20important%20for%20me%20as%20standard%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegoland-new-york-resort-hotel-family-review-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehotel-room%20layouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20usually%20don't%20easily%20accommodate%20a%20family%20of%20five%20like%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20bunk%20beds%20have%20a%20roll-out%20bed%20to%20fit%20three%20kids%20in%20one%20room%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20rare%20in%20my%20traveling%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rooms%20we%20stayed%20at%20had%20a%20kid's%20area%20separate%20from%20a%20space%20for%20adults%2C%20so%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20could%20watch%20television%20or%20read%20a%20book%20without%20fear%20of%20waking%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20hotels%20all%20helped%20keep%20my%20family%20fed%20and%20entertained.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kids%20playing%20with%20Legos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d42b0bb8b41a9673faa8ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20kids%20loved%20seeing%20all%20the%20Lego%20and%20Duplo%20figurines%20at%20the%20hotel's%20lobby.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20into%20the%20rooms%2C%20my%20kids%20squealed%20in%20excitement.%20While%20there%20are%20different%20themes%2C%20we%20were%20always%20assigned%20the%20pirates'%20room.%20There%20are%20also%20Lego%20Dreamz%20and%20Ninjago-themed%20rooms.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20loved%20that%20the%20rooms%20had%20a%20safe%2C%20where%20we%20had%20to%20crack%20a%20code%20by%20answering%20questions%20about%20the%20space%20(for%20example%2C%20how%20many%20ladybugs%20were%20hidden%20in%20it).%20Inside%20the%20safe%2C%20there%20was%20a%20complimentary%20Lego%20set%20for%20each%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20restaurant%20at%20all%20three%20hotels%20that's%20also%20fully%20decorated%20with%20Lego%20characters%20which%20my%20kids%20loved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20wasn't%20that%20impressive%2C%20but%20I%20appreciated%20that%20we%20could%20get%20a%20quick%20bite%20after%20a%20long%20day%20of%20playing%20without%20having%20to%20leave%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAll%20that%20said%2C%20my%20favorite%20park%20was%20Legoland%20Florida.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20at%20Legoland%20Florida%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d3339f69253ccddf99334a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20family%20visited%20Legoland%20Florida%20first.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20all%20three%20parks%20kept%20my%20kids%20entertained%20and%20busy%2C%20my%20personal%20favorite%20was%20the%20one%20in%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20California%20park%20is%20the%20first%20Legoland%20to%20open%20in%20the%20US%2C%20in%201999%2C%20so%20certain%20parts%20of%20it%20feel%20a%20bit%20outdated%20and%20old.%20It's%20also%20smaller%2C%20and%20although%20that%20allowed%20us%20to%20explore%20the%20entire%20property%20(except%20for%20the%20water%20park%20area)%20in%20half%20a%20day%2C%20I%20left%20wanting%20more%20of%20an%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%20fewer%20characters%20walking%20around%2C%20and%20the%20stores%20felt%20pretty%20bare%20bones%20%E2%80%94%20but%20this%20could%20also%20be%20because%20our%20visit%20was%20near%20closing%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20park%20in%20Goshen%20is%20the%20newest%2C%20having%20opened%20in%202021.%20I%20like%20that%20it's%20just%20a%20short%20trip%20away%20from%20New%20York%20City.%20We%20visited%20on%20a%20Friday%2C%20thinking%20it%20would%20be%20less%20crowded%20than%20the%20weekend%2C%20but%20we%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lines%20were%20incredibly%20long%2C%20and%20we%20barely%20got%20to%20do%20any%20attractions.%20We%20later%20found%20out%20that%20day%20was%20a%20school%20holiday%20in%20New%20York%2C%20which%20partially%20explained%20the%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20crowds%20didn't%20feel%20like%20such%20a%20big%20deal%20in%20the%20Florida%20park%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20because%20it's%20the%20biggest%20of%20the%20three.%20It%