4eac5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20liked%20him%20instantly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20one%20thing%20for%20our%20eyes%20to%20meet%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-long-haul-bus-ride-greyhound-miami-seattle-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20crowded%20bus%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20admitting%20that%20he%20was%20tall%2C%20dark%2C%20and%20handsome%20is%20as%20clich%C3%A9d%20as%20it%20gets.%20But%20I%20liked%20him%20instantly%3B%20he%20had%20an%20open%2C%20kind%20face%20and%20a%20calming%20presence.%20The%20most%20surprising%20reaction%20I%20had%20was%20a%20voice%20inside%20my%20head%20that%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20there%20you%20are!%26quot%3B%20as%20if%20I'd%20been%20waiting%20for%20an%20old%20friend%20to%20arrive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I%20dismissed%20this%20because%20it%20sounded%20kooky%20and%20deluded.%20I%20was%2030%2C%20single%2C%20emotionally%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falways-do-a-proper-breakup-with-partner-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebruised%20from%20a%20break-up%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20a%20very%20unsuitable%20person%2C%20and%20in%20the%20process%20of%20packing%20up%20my%20life%20to%20work%20in%20Sydney%2C%2010%2C000%20miles%20away.%20The%20instant%20sense%20of%20ease%20and%20familiarity%20I%20felt%20when%20I%20saw%20Will%20was%20just%20my%20mind%20playing%20tricks.%20I%20naturally%20presumed%20he%20was%20engaged%2Fmarried%2Fcohabiting%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20cross%20my%20mind%20to%20find%20out.%20When%20I%20caught%20his%20eye%2C%20and%20he%20smiled%2C%20I%20smiled%20back%20and%20turned%20away%20(blushing%20furiously).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20that's%20when%20fate%20intervened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a71e525-a085-4658-af29-6f02f901b607%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20asked%20him%20the%20time%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-discontinue-ipod-after-21-years-iconic-music-player-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EiPod%20ran%20out%20of%20battery%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20so%20I%20put%20it%20in%20my%20bag%20and%20took%20out%20my%20phone.%20The%20battery%20had%20also%20died%20%E2%80%94%20odd%2C%20it%20was%20half-full%20when%20I%20left%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%20so%20I%20checked%20my%20watch%20to%20see%20what%20time%20it%20was.%20It%20had%20stopped%20working.%20So%2C%20because%20he%20was%20the%20closest%20person%20to%20me%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20for%20the%20time.%20It%20was%20just%20after%207%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20smiled%2C%20and%20I%20smiled.%20He%20started%20to%20say%20something%2C%20and%20I%20mentally%20willed%20him%20to%20ask%20me%20out%2C%20but%20the%20bus%20pulled%20up%20to%20his%20stop%2C%20and%20he%20shrugged%20apologetically%20and%20got%20off.%20There%20he%20goes%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20back%20to%20the%20lovely%20girlfriend%20I'd%20imagined%20for%20him.%20The%20doors%20closed%2C%20and%20he%20was%20gone.%20The%20bus%20lurched%20forward%2Cd%20and%20I%20said%20my%20goodbyes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoments%20later%2C%20there%20was%20a%20frantic%20knock%20on%20the%20window%2C%20and%20the%20doors%20reopened.%20Will%20pushed%20his%20way%20through%20the%20crowd%20toward%20me.%20He%20said%20he'd%20never%20done%20this%20before%2C%20but%20was%20I%20single%3F%20And%20if%20so%2C%20could%20he%20have%20my%20number%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20we'd%20exchanged%20details%20and%20he'd%20got%20off%20the%20bus%20(again)%2C%20a%20worried-looking%20woman%20warned%20me%20about%20giving%20my%20number%20out%20to%20random%20men.%20I'd%20normally%20agree%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20lived%20in%20the%20city%20long%20enough%20to%20know%20not%20to%20encourage%20strangers%3B%20I%20only%20dated%20men%20I%20met%20through%20friends.%20Instead%2C%20I%20reassured%20her%20that%20he%20wasn't%20a%20weirdo.%20How%20do%20you%20know%2C%20she%20asked.%20I%20just%20did.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aeafce41-a4d1-4b4f-b4c3-c64ee1bf7f02%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20knew%20I%20was%20going%20to%20marry%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20my%20walk%20home%2C%20I%20called%20my%20sister%20and%20said%20I'd%20met%20the%20man%20I%20was%20going%20to%20marry.%20I%20thought%20she'd%20laugh%2C%20but%20she%20didn't%20question%20it.%20Will%20and%20I%20were%20engaged%20five%20months%20later%2C%20and%20the%20following%20Januar%2Cy%20we%20began%20a%20six-month%20trip%20backpacking%20around%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20(that%20was%20the%20compromise%2C%20instead%20of%20me%20working%20abroad%20for%20two%20years).%20We%20married%2C%20and%20have%20been%20together%2021%20years.%20These%20days%2C%20he's%20tall%2C%20gray%20and%20handsome%2C%20which%20is%20fine%20by%20me%2C%20and%20we're%20still%20in%20love.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Couple%20on%20wedding%20day%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1edddb8b41a9673fa75e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221836%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20married%20shortly%20after%20meeting.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20later%20found%20out%20that%20Will%20was%20helping%20a%20friend%20who'd%20moved%20into%20my%20neighborhood%2C%20so%20it%20wasn't%20his%20regular%20route.%20He'd%20chased%20after%20another%20bus%20but%20missed%20it%20by%20seconds%20%E2%80%94%20meanwhile%2C%20I'd%20turned%20down%20a%20post-work%20drink%20(unusual%20move%20on%20my%20part)%20and%20just%20caught%20the%20bus%20we%20both%20took.%20Were%20we%20meant%20to%20be%3F%20I%20like%20to%20think%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2